<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>bus boy • busman</xh5><p> <i>bus boy</i>—(also: busboy) a person whose duty is to clear and reset tables in a restaurant: They felt embarrassed, the way a professional fighter would feel after beating hell out of a <u>bus boy</u>.</p><p><i>busman</i>—the driver of a bus: Mark was an asset to the club with his experience working as a <u>busman</u> in the city.</p><p> <i>See also: boys on the bus, the / man on the bus, the.</i></p> </entry>
